pulses.name: 20250211 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
11 Feb 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:
- United States (US): A significant source, with activity related to AndroxGh0st malware, SystemBC botnet, ZGrab scanning, Censys io scanning, and Back Orifice traffic.
- China (CN): Heavily involved in attacks, specifically targeting NETGEAR DGN1000 devices, D-Link devices, Dasan GPON devices, and exploiting Zivif PR115-204-P-RS web cameras.
- India (IN): Engaged in attacks, particularly targeting D-Link devices, NETGEAR DGN1000 devices, and multiple routers through GPON form login exploits.
